[[Gaar (title)|Gaar]] '''Suppoon''' was a [[Bah'r Kilido]] and also a powerful rival of [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]] who had close relations with the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

==Biography==
Under the alias '''Sonopo Bomoor''', Suppoon committed many atrocities, such as [[Massacre of Bonaka Nueno|attacking]] the [[Intuci|homeworld]] of the man who grew up to become [[Kosh Kurp]], one of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire's]] foremost explosives experts. When [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] wanted to get rid of Suppoon, he merely revealed to Kurp that Suppoon was Sonopo Bomoor, and Kurp turned on Suppoon. Suppoon attempted to defend himself with a [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistol]], but the shot deflected off Kurp's armor and hit Suppoon [[Death/Legends|in the neck]], separating his head from his shoulders.<ref name="JabbaComic" />

